project_descr: Silwan Community Development through the Establishment of the Europ House

outputs.output_descr: The project will contribute to economic and Social welbeing in Silwan Community by promoting women's active participation in social, economical and political life as well as environmental awareness of the local community that suffers from unhealth environmental conditions.  the intervention will focus mainly on Women and Youth of Silwan Community in General, women in particular
